skdetail:

Invocation Name: liverpool football club songs
des:
Liverpool Football Club Songs will bring the song of Anfield right to you. Sing along to the famous, "You'll Never Walk Alone," and get fired up for game day. This skill will warm the hearts of any reds fan and teach your friends and family the lyric of the club. Come on you reds!

Is it game day? Ask Alexa to open Liverpool Football Club Songs and then say, "It's game day!" You will appreciate her response.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
